title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 1500
description:
250 more songs.  This is a re seed of the collection first posted over on KickAss Torrents in October.  The torrent size has been reduced to a quarter to make it more digestible to those who do not know how to torrent and as a direct result suffer from poor download speeds.

The last torrent contained 500 songs in error and the 1500 count will be correct give or take a song or two by the time you download this.   The total collection is over 50,000 songs and will take up just under 300 Gigabytes of hard drive space.

This collection has been re tagged and re file named to industry standard conventions and is designed for correct search results when using a PC or Mac and standard playout software. 

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
